    "It contains the client's needs, circumstances, and constraints to achieve a particular reward goal at a given risk level.",
    "Strategic asset allocation (SAA) is part of this investment policy.",
    "Typically, the SAA is defined as upper and lower boundaries for the asset class allocation.",
    "The risk tolerance and risk capacity also need to be defined.",
    "The second layer of the portfolio management process is the execution layer."
